data.description: Spacious two-story, four-bedroom, three-and-half-bath home with a formal dining room, office with french doors, spacious kitchen, breakfast area, family room, a walk-in pantry, plus a separate butler's pantry.  The second floor features all bedrooms, including the primary bedroom with two walk-in closets, a loft area for yoga or a family room, and a laundry room. Bedroom four features its own bath, perfect for a guest suite. Plus great upgrades: -Three-car garage   - Wood Staircase - Quartz kitchen countertop -Deep sink, gas range upgrade
